x zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529345\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 09, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104krt1665702780879.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/krt1665702780879.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/krt1665702780879.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"krt1665702780879\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Uniface 10: Changes in Subtype Property Inheritance\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"krt1665702780879__unifacechanges_in_subtype_property_inheritance_5293\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">In Uniface 10, property inheritance for subtype entities and fields has changed.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2288e1_d2289e1_d2290e1\">In Uniface 10, subtype entities can inherit properties from their supertypes. In Uniface 9, this behavior was simulated to a limited extent by copying values when the subtype was created. For most properties, subsequent changes to supertype properties were not inherited.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"krt1665702780879__note_w1265ab1b5b5_w1266ab1b5_w1267ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> To ensure compatibility, migrated subtypes continue to use the copied\n         property values, with the exception of properties that cannot be specialized on subtypes or\n         in component entities.For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tre1665702780948.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tre1665702780948.html\" title=\"Values of properties that cannot be specialized in subtype entities or components are cleared during migration.\">Migration of Subtype Properties</a>. </div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"krt1665702780879__topic_d632e1_d633e1_d634e1_d635e1_d636e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d144880e66\">\n                  \n Properties that must be inherited\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2294e1_d2295e1_d2296e1\">The following properties are always inherited and cannot be specialized in the subtype:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d689e1_d690e1_d691e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2297e1_d2298e1_d2299e1\">For subtype entities:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d692e1_d693e1_d694e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mcg1665702702535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mcg1665702702535.html\" title=\"Determines whether the entity is stored in a database. If N, the Data Access and Database Path property values are ignored.\">Database Behavior</a> (U_INDB)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d695e1_d696e1_d697e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cyp1665702702678.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyp1665702702678.html\" title=\"DBMS path to use when storing occurrences of this entity. This is a named route to the Uniface DBMS connector used to connect to the database. Valid values are Uniface default paths ($DEF, $SYS, $UUU), supported databases and file formats, and user-defined paths. The default is DEF.\">Database Path</a> (U_DBMS)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d698e1_d699e1_d700e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a> (U_INT)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d710e1_d711e1_d712e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2300e1_d2301e1_d2302e1\">For subtype fields:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d713e1_d714e1_d715e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aww1665702586248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702586248.html\" title=\"Uniface data type to use for this field, variable, or parameter. The default value is S (String).\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d716e1_d717e1_d718e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a> (U_INT)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d719e1_d720e1_d721e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pta1665702586322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Is External</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"krt1665702780879__topic_d637e1_d638e1_d639e1_d640e1_d641e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d144880e177\">\n                  \n Properties that cannot be inherited\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2306e1_d2307e1_d2308e1\">The following properties cannot be inherited from the supertype because a null value (which normally means the property is inherited) has a special meaning for these properties.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d731e1_d732e1_d733e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2309e1_d2310e1_d2311e1\">For subtype entities:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d734e1_d735e1_d736e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Popup Menu</span> (UPOPUP)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d737e1_d738e1_d739e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">DSP Widget Properties</span> (DSP_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d740e1_d741e1_d742e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">FRM Widget Properties</span> (FRM_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d743e1_d744e1_d745e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">USP Widget Properties</span> (USP_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d746e1_d747e1_d748e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2312e1_d2313e1_d2314e1\">For subtype fields:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d749e1_d750e1_d751e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Initial Value</span> (INITVALUE)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d752e1_d753e1_d754e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Layout</span> (DATA_LAYOUT)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d755e1_d756e1_d757e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field Syntax</span> (DATA_SYNTAX)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d758e1_d759e1_d760e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Value/Representation</span> (VALLAB)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d761e1_d762e1_d763e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Popup Menu</span> (UPOPUP)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d764e1_d765e1_d766e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">DSP Widget Properties</span> (DSP_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d767e1_d768e1_d769e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">FRM Widget Properties</span> (FRM_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"krt1665702780879__li_d770e1_d771e1_d772e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">USP Widget Properties</span> (USP_WIDGETPROPERTIES)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"krt1665702780879__topic_d642e1_d643e1_d644e1_d645e1_d646e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d144880e281\">\n                  \n Properties that can be inherited\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"krt1665702780879__p_d2318e1_d2319e1_d2320e1\">All other properties of subtype entities and fields can be inherited from the supertype. Setting or changing the values in the subtype overrides the inherited value, but will be inherited when the subtype is used in a component.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529345\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529345\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface 10: Changes in Subtype Property Inheritance Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 09, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface 10: Changes in Subtype Property Inheritance In Uniface 10, property inheritance for subtype entities and fields has changed. In Uniface 10, subtype entities can inherit properties from their supertypes. In Uniface 9, this behavior was simulated to a limited extent by copying values when the subtype was created. For most properties, subsequent changes to supertype properties were not inherited. Note: To ensure compatibility, migrated subtypes continue to use the copied property values, with the exception of properties that cannot be specialized on subtypes or in component entities.For more information, see Migration of Subtype Properties . Properties that must be inherited The following properties are always inherited and cannot be specialized in the subtype: For subtype entities: Database Behavior (U_INDB) Database Path (U_DBMS) Database Interface (Entities) (U_INT) For subtype fields: Data Type Database Interface (Entities) (U_INT) Is External Properties that cannot be inherited The following properties cannot be inherited from the supertype because a null value (which normally means the property is inherited) has a special meaning for these properties. For subtype entities: Popup Menu (UPOPUP) DSP Widget Properties (DSP_WIDGETPROPERTIES) FRM Widget Properties (FRM_WIDGETPROPERTIES) USP Widget Properties (USP_WIDGETPROPERTIES) For subtype fields: Initial Value (INITVALUE) Field Layout (DATA_LAYOUT) Field Syntax (DATA_SYNTAX) Value/Representation (VALLAB) Popup Menu (UPOPUP) DSP Widget Properties (DSP_WIDGETPROPERTIES) FRM Widget Properties (FRM_WIDGETPROPERTIES) USP Widget Properties (USP_WIDGETPROPERTIES) Properties that can be inherited All other properties of subtype entities and fields can be inherited from the supertype. Setting or changing the values in the subtype overrides the inherited value, but will be inherited when the subtype is used in a component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}